-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Attribution
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project is a Delphi/Object Pascal implementation derived from the
reference C VM ("clox") presented in *Crafting Interpreters* by Robert Nystrom
(https://craftinginterpreters.com/). The original clox source is released
under the MIT License, Copyright (c) 2015 Robert Nystrom, and remains
available at https://github.com/munificent/craftinginterpreters.

The architecture (bytecode chunk layout, stack-based dispatch, NaN-boxed
values, Pratt-style single-pass compiler, mark-sweep GC, hash-table based
globals) follows that book. Pascal-specific extensions in this repository are original work covered by the MIT
license above.
